   sql:select g.*,um.name username,s.name schoolname from goods g join users u on u.id =g.uid join users_msg um on um.id=u.mid join school s on um.school=s.id where g.id=NULL

   sql:select g.*,um.name username,s.name schoolname,t.name tagname from goods g join tags t on t.id=g.tag join users u on u.id =g.uid join users_msg um on um.id=u.mid join school s on um.school=s.id where g.id='22'
   result:[]

   sql:select g.*,um.name username,s.name schoolname,t.name tagname from goods g join tags t on t.id=g.tag join users u on u.id =g.uid join users_msg um on um.id=u.mid join school s on um.school=s.id where g.id='22'
